question: UFC 287: Who will win - Pereira or Adesanya?
description:
UFC 287 is an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that is scheduled to take place on April 8, 2023, at the Miami-Dade Arena in Miami, Florida, USA.

This is a market on whether Alex Pereira or Israel Adesanya will win their bout.

If Alex Pereira is declared the winner of this bout, this market will resolve to “Pereira”. If Israel Adesanya is declared the winner of this bout, this market will resolve to “Adesanya”.

If this fight is declared a draw, or if for any reason the match is not scored, postponed after April 15, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, or cancelled, this market will resolve 50-50.

question: UFC 287: Will Israel Adesanya win by finish?
description:
UFC 287 is an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that is scheduled to take place on April 8, 2023, at the Miami-Dade Arena in Miami, Florida, USA.

This is a market on whether Israel Adesanya will win his upcoming bout with Alex Pereira by finish. To "win by finish" means winning by KO/TKO/disqualification, submission, or any other form of stoppage. Any decision made by the judges will not count as a finish.

This market will resolve to “Yes” if Israel Adesanya wins his UFC 287 bout with Alex Pereira by finish. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If this fight is declared a draw, or if for any reason the match is not scored, postponed after April 15, 2023, 11:59:59 PM ET, or cancelled, this market will resolve 50-50.
